creator: Perk Apps
descriptionHtml:
Every day is a fresh start. Stay fresh, relax, calm, and focused with Sleep sounds

Sleep Music - Relax, Sleep, Meditate offer a fantastic assortment of HD sleep sounds, White noise, relax melodies, and sleep music that can be re-combined to create the ideal calm atmosphere for sleeping.

Beat Insomnia with Sleep meditation sounds


You can select from a variety of sleep sounds like rain sounds, nature sounds, city sounds, white noise, or relax melodies. Save your favorite sleep music mixes to have them with you everywhere.

Highlight Features
✅ Create custom mixes
✅ Auto-off timer
✅ Sleep sound categories and sub-categories
✅ Favorites list
✅ Ocean, Rain, Wind, Fire & Oriental (Main categories)
✅ Block disruptive sounds, get an uninterrupted sleep

Sleep Music - Relax, Sleep, Meditate helps with:
🌟 Falling asleep quickly
🌟 Beats insomnia
🌟 Elevate mood
🌟 Fresh mind
🌟 Concentration
🌟 Customization
🌟 Reduce anxiety and reduce tension

Sleep Music - Relax, Sleep, Meditate is like your sleeping partner that helps you fall asleep instantly, reduces anxiety, makes you focused. Sleep well, beat insomnia, and boost your mood with relax melodies in this Sleep sounds app. During use, you can customize your sleeping music or you can choose from already mixed melody music for you.

It has sleep sounds of nature like ocean, rain, wind, fire, and oriental as main categories and has other sub-categories related to the main sleep sounds group.

You can set a timer on sleep meditation nature sounds to automatically shut down the Sleep Music - Relax, Sleep, Meditate. Sleep sounds do not require an internet connection, so you may enjoy sleep music wherever you want to calm and relax without having to worry about data usage.

Your suggestions?
Sleep music is solely for you guys, so, if you have any suggestions or questions, please contact us. We can improve/update this app for you!

We make sure to give you the best sleep experience with sleep sounds, nature sounds, meditation sounds, white noise, and many other sounds that can help you relax, focus, and get a good meditation sleep, so that you can start everyday day with fresh mind and body 😊


Happy Sleeping!
descriptionShort: Win over insomnia with Sleep sounds, nature sounds, rain sounds & white noise
